description: Citizens Bancorp Investment, Inc. provides various banking products and services in Tennessee. The company offers checking and savings accounts, certificates of deposits and individual retirement accounts, credit and debit cards, overdrafts, real-time processing, and online and mobile banking services, as well as cash management, and personal and business services for individuals and businesses. It also provides personal, mortgage, construction, agriculture, commercial, and officers loans, as well as wealth management services. The company serves in Bedford, Clay, Coffee, DeKalb, Franklin, Jackson, Macon, Overton, Putnam, Smith, Sumner, and Wilson and surrounding counties in Middle Tennessee through 22 banking offices. Citizens Bancorp Investment, Inc. was founded in 1909 and is based in Lafayette, Tennessee.
